{"type":null,"faqId":7571,"title":"如何添加/删除共享文件？","answer":"<p>点击打开&ldquo;我的共享文件&rdquo;，点击菜单键<img style=\"WIDTH: 40px; HEIGHT: 37px\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"45\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/0-111125152536.PNG\" />弹出添加共享文件的操作菜单。如下图所示：</p>\n<p><img style=\"WIDTH: 390px; HEIGHT: 407px\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"496\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/1-111125152548.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>点击打开已共享的文件，可看到已共享的文件列表，点击相应的媒体文件可进行播放。</p>\n<p>添加共享文件<br />点击&ldquo;添加共享文件&rdquo;，即可进入本地文件文件管理器，选中其中的媒体文件或含有媒体文件的文件夹，点击&ldquo;共享&rdquo;，即完成了共享文件的添加。<br />如何删除共享文件<br />点击&ldquo;多选&rdquo;，然后选中欲删除文件后的方框，如下图所示：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" width=\"426\" height=\"186\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/2-111125152606.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>也可以单击&ldquo;清除全部共享&rdquo;的方式删除所有共享文件。<br />备注：在共享文件时应在设置<img style=\"WIDTH: 48px; HEIGHT: 57px\" alt=\"\" width=\"65\" height=\"76\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/3-111125152637.PNG\" />中将共享我的文件选项选中，如下图所示，否则其他设备在搜索&ldquo;周边设备&rdquo;时就不能搜索到该手机。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" width=\"360\" height=\"135\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/4-111125152650.PNG\" /></p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7711","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1322015318000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":4332,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":66,"times":15,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":4.4,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}